00:31:21.915 --> 00:31:24.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you won't defend yourself,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're not going to testify.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:31:24.914 --> 00:31:27.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a hearing, not a trial.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:31:27.993 --> 00:31:29.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She has no choice.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:31:38.910 --> 00:31:40.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:31:41.669 --> 00:31:43.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo's on subspace.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:31:43.309 --> 00:31:44.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's urgent.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:31:48.787 --> 00:31:50.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I've made some progress.</i></c.bg_transparent>

541
00:31:50.307 --> 00:31:51.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:31:51.826 --> 00:31:53.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Not good.</i></c.bg_transparent>

543
00:31:53.506 --> 00:31:56.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Since the transmission</i></c.bg_transparent>
