554
00:32:23.456 --> 00:32:26.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-The wife.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-The wife.</i></c.bg_transparent>

555
00:32:28.735 --> 00:32:31.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon Dax and Enina Tandro.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:32:32.934 --> 00:32:34.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Maybe it was innocent.</i></c.bg_transparent>

557
00:32:34.413 --> 00:32:36.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Maybe he was just providing</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>a little emotional support</i></c.bg_transparent>

558
00:32:36.853 --> 00:32:38.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>during tough times.</i></c.bg_transparent>

559
00:32:38.652 --> 00:32:40.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Or maybe they were taking advantage</i></c.bg_transparent>

560
00:32:40.932 --> 00:32:43.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>of the General's absence</i></c.bg_transparent>
