561
00:32:44.130 --> 00:32:45.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>If they were having an affair,</i></c.bg_transparent>

562
00:32:45.850 --> 00:32:49.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>that translates into a pretty</i></c.bg_transparent>
