563
00:33:00.457 --> 00:33:01.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The conversations were just the beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:33:01.806 --> 00:33:03.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've also found records of gifts,</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:33:03.644 --> 00:33:06.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of holidays spent at an inn</c.bg_transparent>
