567
00:33:08.437 --> 00:33:10.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It serves the truth.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, the truth.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:33:10.523 --> 00:33:12.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If there's more to this</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than meets the eye,</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:33:12.202 --> 00:33:13.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope you'll explain,</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:33:13.442 --> 00:33:16.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because as it stands</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this will severely hurt Dax's defense.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:33:20.560 --> 00:33:23.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My husband was not the hero in life</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:33:23.238 --> 00:33:25.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that he was in death, Mr. Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:33:26.318 --> 00:33:28.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In death, he became a legend</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:33:28.517 --> 00:33:30.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I became a legend's wife.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:33:30.516 --> 00:33:32.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are people who did not</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even know my husband</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:33:32.955 --> 00:33:34.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>who still contact me.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:33:34.755 --> 00:33:37.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Decades after his death,</c.bg_transparent>
