578
00:33:37.835 --> 00:33:38.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you don't.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:33:38.954 --> 00:33:43.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, because I knew the man</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before he became a legend.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:33:43.193 --> 00:33:45.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I also know my place in history.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:33:45.632 --> 00:33:48.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My place is to carry on bravely,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>never to remarry,</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:33:48.951 --> 00:33:52.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to represent my husband at the banquets</c.bg_transparent>
