583
00:33:52.150 --> 00:33:55.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But never, never to talk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about who he really was.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:33:56.149 --> 00:33:58.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because nobody wants to hear that.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:33:59.868 --> 00:34:01.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They may have to hear it now.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:34:03.386 --> 00:34:07.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No matter what is said,</c.bg_transparent>
