587
00:34:10.585 --> 00:34:14.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For he was and always will be</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:34:15.943 --> 00:34:18.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the hero who died for his people.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:34:23.700 --> 00:34:27.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But perhaps it's time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for my place in history to change.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:34:35.573 --> 00:34:37.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been protecting her reputation.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:34:37.576 --> 00:34:39.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

592
