<c.bg_transparent>That's why you won't even defend yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:34:47.973 --> 00:34:51.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are worse things</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than an illicit love affair.</c.bg_transparent>

594
