<c.bg_transparent>Curzon didn't murder anybody.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:34:53.932 --> 00:34:56.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He didn't commit treason.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:34:56.730 --> 00:35:01.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you really willing to commit suicide</c.bg_transparent>
