597
00:35:01.169 --> 00:35:03.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That is what you're doing, you know.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:35:06.768 --> 00:35:08.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My God, Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:35:08.407 --> 00:35:11.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Young Tandro... That wouldn't be your son?</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:35:11.872 --> 00:35:13.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have an overactive imagination,</c.bg_transparent>
