601
00:35:13.766 --> 00:35:16.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then what is it that's holding you back?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Help me.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:35:18.205 --> 00:35:19.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:35:19.284 --> 00:35:21.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Damn it, if you were still a man...</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:35:22.843 --> 00:35:23.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( bangs wall )</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:35:27.242 --> 00:35:29.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see your temper hasn't improved.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:35:29.441 --> 00:35:31.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't talk to me about my temper.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:35:31.811 --> 00:35:32.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon always warned you about it.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:35:32.840 --> 00:35:35.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to get me off track here.</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:35:36.639 --> 00:35:40.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you remember that Argosian Lieutenant</c.bg_transparent>
