610
00:35:42.780 --> 00:35:45.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:35:46.475 --> 00:35:49.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you knocked me down with a right cross</c.bg_transparent>
