613
00:35:57.472 --> 00:36:01.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I tried on that ring after Curzon died.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:36:03.111 --> 00:36:05.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It just slipped off my finger.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:36:07.990 --> 00:36:12.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't help me, old man,</c.bg_transparent>
