616
00:36:12.148 --> 00:36:14.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>because I don't know any more arguments.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:36:16.747 --> 00:36:18.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then allow it to happen.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:36:18.946 --> 00:36:22.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is my obligation to protect the lives</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of those in my command.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:36:22.944 --> 00:36:25.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You ought to know that,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you taught it to me.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:36:26.824 --> 00:36:28.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
