621
00:36:28.983 --> 00:36:30.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll stop trying to protect you</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:36:30.782 --> 00:36:33.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
