00:36:33.862 --> 00:36:35.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't discuss it with you.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:36:36.616 --> 00:36:37.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As for Enina Tandro</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:36:38.203 --> 00:36:42.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>yes, I feel the shame</c.bg_transparent>
