626
00:36:43.459 --> 00:36:46.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When one of my kind stumbles, Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:36:46.178 --> 00:36:48.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it is a mistake that's there forever.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:36:49.977 --> 00:36:52.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
