630
00:36:57.494 --> 00:37:01.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can tell you... that he did love her</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:37:02.653 --> 00:37:04.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for whatever that's worth.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:37:05.523 --> 00:37:06.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enough to kill her husband?</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:37:08.891 --> 00:37:10.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you are questioning?</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:37:11.410 --> 00:37:13.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What else can I do?</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:37:14.929 --> 00:37:17.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:37:17.209 --> 00:37:18.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing at all.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:37:34.403 --> 00:37:38.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant Dax, you are either</c.bg_transparent>
