639
00:37:42.521 --> 00:37:45.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At first,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I wondered which of those you were.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:37:45.321 --> 00:37:49.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, I am bothered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by the likelihood that you may be both.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:37:52.958 --> 00:37:54.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's finish this, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:37:56.357 --> 00:38:01.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At what age did the host, Jadzia</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>first want to be joined as a Trill?</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:38:01.196 --> 00:38:04.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted it since I was a child.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I worked very hard for it.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:38:04.355 --> 00:38:07.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The competition to become</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a Trill is very strong, then,</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:38:07.354 --> 00:38:08.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>among potential hosts?</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:38:08.993 --> 00:38:11.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes. It's considered a great honor.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:38:11.272 --> 00:38:14.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did the young Jadzia finally</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>become a host candidate?</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:38:14.311 --> 00:38:18.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>By winning scholarships,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>competing against other young people.</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:38:18.310 --> 00:38:19.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're tested in countless ways.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:38:19.990 --> 00:38:21.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Including psychological tests</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:38:21.469 --> 00:38:23.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to determine strength of character</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the prospective host.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:38:23.588 --> 00:38:24.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that true?</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:38:25.188 --> 00:38:26.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:38:26.388 --> 00:38:31.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the young Jadzia excelled in those</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tests of academics and character--</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:38:31.346 --> 00:38:32.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of psychological stability.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:38:34.659 --> 00:38:35.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:38:36.225 --> 00:38:40.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you can remember other things,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>remember that as well.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:38:42.903 --> 00:38:45.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What academic degrees do you hold,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant?</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:38:46.742 --> 00:38:51.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hold Premier Distinctions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in exobiology, zoology,</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:38:52.608 --> 00:38:55.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>astrophysics, and exoarchaeology.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:38:55.339 --> 00:38:59.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How many of those degrees did you earn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before being joined with the symbiont Dax?</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:39:00.178 --> 00:39:01.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of them.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:39:01.698 --> 00:39:03.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of them.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:39:04.577 --> 00:39:05.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:39:06.566 --> 00:39:06.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alone.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:39:09.535 --> 00:39:12.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This brilliant and independent</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>young woman</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:39:12.774 --> 00:39:16.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>has done nothing in her life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but contribute to her society.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:39:16.493 --> 00:39:19.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Arbiter, how can anyone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>justify trying her for a crime</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:39:20.123 --> 00:39:23.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>allegedly committed by another entity</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before she was even born?</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:39:26.610 --> 00:39:28.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This will only take a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:39:29.929 --> 00:39:31.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant...</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:39:31.569 --> 00:39:33.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>as a Trill candidate,</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:39:33.448 --> 00:39:36.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>did Jadzia fully understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the responsibilities</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:39:36.167 --> 00:39:38.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to be assumed upon becoming a Trill,</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:39:38.167 --> 00:39:40.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and did you willingly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>accept those responsibilities</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:39:40.606 --> 00:39:43.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and whatever consequences</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they might entail?</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:39:43.804 --> 00:39:44.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:39:45.444 --> 00:39:47.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And would that not obviously</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>include the consequences</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:39:47.683 --> 00:39:50.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of criminal acts committed by Curzon Dax?</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:39:50.363 --> 00:39:51.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opening )</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:40:01.639 --> 00:40:03.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I speak?</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:40:03.199 --> 00:40:04.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you are?</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:40:05.838 --> 00:40:07.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am Enina Tandro,</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:40:07.837 --> 00:40:10.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>widow of General Ardelon Tandro.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:40:11.157 --> 00:40:12.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This hearing is unnecessary.</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:40:12.916 --> 00:40:14.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The accusations are erroneous.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:40:14.756 --> 00:40:16.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mother, what are you talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:40:18.154 --> 00:40:19.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Arbiter,</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:40:19.554 --> 00:40:22.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon Dax is accused</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:40:22.273 --> 00:40:26.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of sending a transmission to the enemy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that betrayed my husband.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:40:28.111 --> 00:40:30.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I know where Curzon was</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:40:30.751 --> 00:40:33.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>at the exact time</c.bg_transparent>
