693
00:40:37.268 --> 00:40:40.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was... in my bed.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:40:59.542 --> 00:41:00.901 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. Tandro,</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:41:00.981 --> 00:41:04.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you will want to reexamine</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your extradition request.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:41:05.740 --> 00:41:06.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Until then,</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:41:07.197 --> 00:41:09.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>this hearing is adjourned.</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:41:22.558 --> 00:41:25.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was kind of you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to try and protect me...</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:41:26.294 --> 00:41:28.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>someone you'd never even met.</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:41:28.733 --> 00:41:31.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's much of Curzon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's still a part of me,</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:41:31.692 --> 00:41:35.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that still remembers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you had together.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:41:35.131 --> 00:41:38.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But it was Curzon Dax</c.bg_transparent>
