703
00:41:38.770 --> 00:41:42.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to preserve the memory</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of General Tandro, not Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:41:43.169 --> 00:41:46.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I felt it was important</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to keep that promise.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:41:46.688 --> 00:41:50.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The General's memory</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is cherished by your people.</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:41:50.806 --> 00:41:53.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And it will continue to be.</c.bg_transparent>

707
00:41:54.166 --> 00:41:58.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, no one will ever know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that he was the one who tried to betray us</c.bg_transparent>

708
00:41:58.524 --> 00:42:01.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and that the rebels</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>killed him for the favor.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:42:04.522 --> 00:42:09.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As for you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there is one favor I would ask.</c.bg_transparent>

710
00:42:10.201 --> 00:42:12.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:42:13.120 --> 00:42:15.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Live, Jadzia Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:42:24.476 --> 00:42:27.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Live a long, fresh, and wonderful life.</c.bg_transparent>

